ny, saying it was meant to celebrate diversity and pay tribute to feasting and French gastronomy.\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3429, \"end\": 3435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9999994576384431, \"rank\": 5.420561523764715e-07, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}, {\"begin\": 3590, \"end\": 3596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9901115954982238, \"rank\": 0.008584807068927777, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ceremony's artistic director\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3428}, {\"ngram\": \"his scene\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3461}, {\"ngram\": \"any \\\"Last Supper\\\" parallels\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3494}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3557}, {\"ngram\": \"tribute\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps was asked about the outcry during an International Olympic Committee news conference on Sunday.\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3609, \"end\": 3619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2042580661229345e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3638, \"end\": 3646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}, {\"begin\": 3684, \"end\": 3715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the outcry\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3673}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 3769, \"to\": 3781}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the contrary, I think (with) Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance,\\\" Descamps said.\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3924, \"end\": 3932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the contrary\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3840}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 3902, \"to\": 3921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 4034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 3961}, {\"ngram\": \"the polls\", \"from\": 3965, \"to\": 3974}, {\"ngram\": \"this ambition\", \"from\": 4007, \"to\": 4020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense we are, of cours